<plot>Incidents of chance and circumstance through-out his life has warped the mind of comic-book store owner Lloyd Hamlin. He believes he possesses the same powers of his beloved superheroes and has dedicated his life to defend the world against evil. It is only until a curious news reporter interviews Lloyd that we realize Lloyd's fantasy may be more reality than fiction.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?251969</url></doc>
